        <h2 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl title-font font-medium text-gray-900 mt-4 mb-4">89 lakh kids below 5 years given polio drops across India on 'Polio Ravivar': Health ministry</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-8 ">New Delhi: Around 89 lakh children under five years of age, as per provisional data, were given polio drops across the country on Sunday on the occasion of Polio National Immunization Day, also known as 'Polio Ravivar', the Union health ministry said. The vaccination was done at around 7 lakh booths which were staffed with 12 lakh vaccinators and 1.8 lakh supervisors.</p>
